metadata.name: Zhang TIANSHI SAID
metadata.description:
pass OVER, LIU YIYI took both hands, "Thank you!"



"Yiyi, you should have a heart of treading on thin ice in your practice, and you must not be hasty. I don't know how you can make such rapid progress but still have a solid foundation. But you are still young, so it is always right to practice slowly and polish the foundation carefully." Before he left, Master Zhang could not help saying a word.
